metadata.name: Freddy the Fud-muppet
metadata.description:
meet Freddy the FUD-muppet, everything he touch goes to zero and he believes deep in his heart that he's not gonna make it, his wife left him for Kermit the frog. after she found out that Freddy was a nft Boy. Freddy got rekt during the bear market. his life spiraling down a trench of shame and despair, burning down everything what across his path.  
This is a special 1/1 edition
